Since a split king adjustable foundation raises/lowers both sides of the bed independently, kind of mattress do I need to purchase if I went with a split king adjustable foundation?



GeneG



                            on Jun 4, 2016
                        








BEST ANSWER: The Adjustable Bed & Mattress are sold separately. At the top of PlushBeds' website, there is a tab for Adjustable Foundations & a separate tab for Mattresses. We have 5 Adjustable Bed models. Once you decide which one you want, add it to your basket & then click on the Mattress tab at the top of the page. We have natural latex, memory foam, cool gel and encased coil mattresses. All of our mattresses work well with our Adjustable Beds. Just click on the size tab to order the same size mattress as your Adjustable Bed.

Reply

Inaccurate



            Dawn H
        

