The Botanical Bliss™ 100% All Natural Latex Mattress.



														When you upgrade to today's luxury mattress standards, you'll want a bed that's 100% natural, chemical free, 
														luxuriously comfortable, and long-lasting. Our slideshow will explain why we give you the quality, luxury, 
														and eco-friendly comfort that no other mattress company can.
													

  
You're about to see why after comparison shopping for a chemical free 100% natural mattress, more people choose 
														our Botanical Bliss™ 100% natural latex mattress over any other brand. PlushBeds gives you what no other mattress 
														can...an organically pure sleep surface and a clear conscience.













1. The Botanical Bliss™ latex mattress collection only contains 100% certified natural latex


While most "Latex Mattresses" sold today are promoted as "100% latex", but contain synthetic latex made from petrochemical products which have limited elasticity, Plushbeds is proud to offer 100% Natural Sri Lankan Botanical Latex with no synthetic blends or petroleum based products. With a more dense, supportive 100% natural dunlop core to prevent sagging and a less-dense top layer of 100% natural talalay latex for maximum pressure relief, you receive a mattress that offers optimized pressure relief and uncompromising support, resulting in deeper, restorative sleep.

  
	The Botanical Bliss™latex mattress offers the perfect combination of resilient support and pressure relief that can only be found with a solid 100% natural latex mattress.













2. PlushBeds offers the softest, finest quality Organic Cotton online.


Aside from the latex used in the mattress, the mattress cover is the next most important, yet most overlooked component to compare. Several online mattress retailers boast the use of organic cotton; however fail to mention its the cheaper, mass-produced woven organic cotton. Woven fabrics are tight, course and do not stretch, hindering the pressure-relieving benefits of natural latex.

  
	PlushBeds exclusive knitted mattress covers are softer, more breathable, more elastic, offer better moisture control, and provide better pressure relief than the mass produced woven covers used by our competitors.













3. Our Botanical Bliss™ uses a Pure New Zealand Wool fire barrier.



															Unlike competitors who use harsh fire retardants, our Botanical Bliss covers are created with soft Pure New Zealand Wool. 
															The Botanical Bliss mattress is ideal for those who suffer from feather, down, or synthetic bedding products 
															allergies. Our quilted mattress covers are naturally fire-resistant, ensure natural temperature regulation, are hypoallergenic, 
															antimicrobial, and are dust mite resistant.
														

  

																Our Botanical Bliss mattresses are protected by all-natural, Pure New Zealand Wool for its supportive qualities 
																to extra sensitive allergy requirements, as well as for its softness and comfort.
															














												4. No Smelly Glues...or adhesives of any kind. Our layers of natural latex are removable to adjust comfort.
											



														True 100% natural latex doesn't need to be glued; competitors who glue their layers may not be using 100% natural latex. 
														PlushBeds offers removable, adjustable layers so you can simply unzip your cover and rotate your layers of latex to adjust 
														the firmness of your mattress.
													

  
With un-glued latex layers, you can easily adjust your mattress firmness by changing a layer of latex without having to 
														return the whole mattress














												5. PlushBeds has a Rock Solid Reputation
											



														When you buy a natural latex mattress, you are making an investment in your sleep, your bodys revitalization, and your health. Like any investment, it's wise to look at the reputation of the company you are considering buying from. Are they an accredited business with the Better Business Bureau? How many complaints have been filed against them by other customers before you? This can be easily found by going to the Better Business Bureau and entering the name of the companies you've considered. A company's past track record is a good indication of what you might expect should problems arise after you've made your purchase.
													

  

															PlushBeds has a rock solid reputation and hundreds of readable reviews from verified customers.
														














												6. 4 different firmnesses available on every Botanical Bliss mattress.
											



														PlushBeds is not just a mattress retailer, but also the manufacturer. This gives us a broad range of options in the comfort levels we can offer. Where most internet retailers are limited to a single firmness per mattress model, PlushBeds offers 4 different firmnesses for each latex mattress we sell. Additionally, because each mattress is custom made, we can accommodate virtually any request. Need a specific height or specific firmness (ILD) that you don't see online? Just give is a call, and we'll be glad to assist in building a custom-made latex mattress that is just right for you.
													

  

															All Botanical Blis™ latex mattresses are available in 4 different firmnesses and are custom made, offering you more options to choosing the perfect mattress.
														














												7. 100 Night Comfort Exchange Program
											



														Wherever you decide to buy your latex mattress from, we hope you choose the correct firmness the first time around, but what if it's too soft or too firm? Most online companies glue their layers together, in fact, as many as 4 cups of glue are used in a single "all natural" latex mattress. If the firmness is not what you had hoped, what are your options? Your only option is to re-package the mattress and ship it back. The PlushBeds comfort exchange program offers an affordable and convenient solution to adjusting your mattress firmness without the hassle of having to return the whole mattress.
													

 

													Free of any shipping fees, we'll send you a new layer of natural latex in a different firmness, which 9 times out of 10 will solve a comfort issue without having to return your mattress.
														














												8. Easy, 100 Night FREE Mattress Returns
											



														If after 30 days you decide that your Plushbeds latex mattress is not for you, just call us within your first 100 nights and we'll pick up the mattress and bonus items for a full refund of your purchase price. Many competitors tell you they will "take the mattress back" but you will be required to pay return shipping costs ($300 - $500), restocking fees, or "damage fees", to be determined by the company after they receive your mattress back
													

 

														Every Botanical Bliss™ latex mattress comes with our famous 100 night Free return policy. We'll pay the return shipping costs for a curbside pickup, and you'll receive a full refund of your purchase price.
														














												9. Industry's Strongest 25 Year Warranty
											



														Plushbeds guarantees that your latex mattress will be replaced or repaired at our option, should it be deemed defective because of faulty workmanship or structural defects for a period of 25 years beginning on the date of delivery, with 100% coverage for 10 full years, and pro-rated in years 11-25. The latex mattresses we deliver to our customers are the same latex mattresses we sleep on ourselves, which is why we are proud to offer the strongest 25 year manufacturer's warranty in the industry.
													

  

																
													All Botanical Bliss™ latex mattresses are protected for 25 years from faulty workmanship or structural defects.
														














												10. It's the Latex Mattress Recommended by Professionals
											



														Our 100% natural latex mattresses are often recommended by orthopedic specialists and chiropractors. 
													The mix of pressure -relieving softness and buoyant support offered by our hypo-allergenic natural construction makes botanical latex an ideal bedding material. Don't settle for a synthetic or hybrid option when choosing all-natural botanical latex can prove to be one of the best investments for your health and longevity. 
													

														A latex mattress isn't a cure-all, and a website recommendation should never replace a visit to your doctor.
													

 

															Our 100% natural latex mattresses are often recommended by orthopedic specialists and chiropractors because of the unequaled support they provide.
														
















