Love our mattress!!!
We were incredibly hesitant to purchase a mattress online, but all of the positive reviews convinced my husband and I to take a leap of faith and we are so glad we did! We got the 9" Botanical Bliss in Medium/Firm with the orthopedic foundation. We are side and back sleepers and the support has been great for both of us. We've been sleeping on our new mattress for 4 months now and we're amazed at how much more comfortable it has been in comparison to our old innerspring pillowtop mattress. No more restless, sleepless nights, no more pain and discomfort in the morning, and no more allergies!! Side note, the unboxing process is pretty amusing--- so crazy that they can squeeze a queen sized mattress into such a tiny box! Just a heads up, the mattress is a bit heavy and floppy, so it's not easy to move around once it's rolled out. The foundation is sturdy and we were able to assemble it quickly and easily. The included supportive latex pillows and super soft Egyptian cotton sheets were an awesome added bonus! Our bed is sooooo comfy now and we would highly recommend giving a PlushBeds mattress a try. 5 stars all around for ultimate comfort, quality products, great value, fast shipping, and excellent customer service!



