Everything I was looking for!
I searched for MONTHS....researching mattresses! My old mattress was made in the traditional poly foam....TERRIBLE!  I slept so terribly hot and was awake all nite long...trying to cool off.  In my research I learned that latex does not hold heat....and it proved itself 100%!  I am about 2 weeks into this new mattress....and I haven't slept so well in years!  I am extremely happy!!!  I ordered medium firm....and it is not at all too stiff. It supports as well as gives.  LOVE IT!  Yes I would definitely recommend this mattress and have!  My only dislike...was in the pillows that did come with the bed. They were shreaded latex and I am a solid latex pillow sleeper...but I did want to try them to compare.  I think they would be fine for many, but because I have ALWAYS been a solid latex pillow person....it just didn't compare for me.  Great experience in all!



