9Inch Botanical Bliss
This mattress is a dream come true. 29-31 is firm enough for me.  I am 160 pounds, try to loose some, but this firmness is for  250pounds.  It is great support for my back.  I used to cry and scream during many nights because of spasm in my both legs.  Since I sleep on the 9" Botanical Bliss I have not have to cry or scream since.  If you are looking for new mattress go with Botanical Bliss, because their price is better.  The one 1" of wool on top of mattress and gooses down comforter will make your body feel nice and warm.  Looking for combination 29-31 with a 2" medium on top will take you to heaven whole night long.  Good luck and share your experience if you try my combination. I would love to hear it.



