Specialized Products
                Leggett & Platt's specialized products can be found in numerous markets. In the automotive industry, we're the world's foremost designer and manufacturer of seating support and comfort systems. We are also a major supplier of titanium, nickel, and stainless steel tubing for the aerospace industry. Finally, we manufacture and install a variety of products for commercial vehicle use.
                


