Business Segments


                    Leggett & Platt's diverse manufacturing capabilities are divided into four product segments: Residential Products – We are a leading supplier of a wide range of components used in finished bedding and residential settings; Furniture Products – We create products and components for the home and office; Industrial Products – Our own steel rod mill produces the steel used in our myriad wire products; Specialized Products – We feature products in a diverse array of specialty applications, from vehicle seat support to aerospace products.
                


ResidentialProducts
IndustrialProducts
FurnitureProducts
SpecializedProducts





                                Leggett & Platt's heritage and leadership in the residential furnishings industry span more than 130 years. We produce state-of-the-art quilting, sewing, and machinery for the bedding industry and are the leading supplier of a wide range of products and components for the home, including mattress springs and carpet cushion, as well as bedding machinery and erosion-control products.
                            





Davor Gecic – Managing Director, Division VP






Go to Residential Products





                                Leggett & Platt is the country's leading producer of drawn steel wire. Six plants produce hundreds of thousands of tons of steel wire every year, half of which is used internally in the production of our own products. Other operations produce specialty wire products, including shaped wire and coated wire products. 
                            





Lucretia Burt – Sales Administrator






Go to Industrial Products





                                Leggett & Platt is the leading supplier of products and components for the home. Our products in the Furniture Products category include: adjustable bed bases, ornamental headboards and footboards, bed frames, bedding accessories, seat recliner mechanisms and controls, sleepers, lifts, seating components, furniture bases, curved plywood, and components for office furniture manufacturers.
                            





Jay Thompson – President, Adjustable Bed Group






Go to Furniture Products





                                Leggett & Platt's diverse array of specialized products includes automotive seating support structures and comfort systems, a category in which we're the world's foremost designer and manufacturer; steel tubing for the aerospace industry; and, finally, commercial vehicle products.
                            





Dan Culbertson – Division Controller






