Company segments[edit]
Residential Products[edit]
Leggett & Platt provides a variety of components and machinery used by bedding manufacturers in the production and assembly of their finished products. Leggett & Platt also produces and distributes carpet cushion for residential and commercial applications. In addition, they are a major distributor of geo components used in ground stabilization, drainage protection, erosion control, and weed control.[1]
