Specialized Products[edit]
Leggett & Platt is a designer and manufacturer of automotive seating support, pneumatic and mechanical lumbar systems. They are also a supplier of titanium, nickel, and stainless steel tubing to the aerospace industry. It is a supplier of service van interiors used in commercial vehicles.
