What is the difference between the Split King and King sizes in the Adjustable Foundation?



                            A shopper
                            


                            on Oct 11, 2015
                        











SCape Adjustable Bed�



Reverie 8Q Adjustable Bed



Reverie 5D Adjustable Bed



Prodigy Adjustable Bed�



Premiere Adjustable Bed











BEST ANSWER: The king sized Adjustable Foundation moves as one piece via remote control. The split king sized Adjustable Foundation comes with two remote controls and each side of the bed can move independently with its own remote control.

