Fantastic Bed. Natural 100% Certified natural latex with no nasty chemical smell. Smells fresh and natural when opened up. Very easy setup, just unroll, add your topper, get those organic sheets on and enjoy the comfort with the added latex shredded pillows for perfect support of the neck and spine. My synthetic foam mattress went straight to the curb after sitting in the living room for just a day. That's how long it took me to realize this was the best purchase I made for my health. One third of your life is spent on a mattress sleeping, why wouldn't you want to sleep healthily without breathing toxic voc's with synthetic made chemicals. The liquid proof mattress cover is a nice bonus incase my puppy has an accident. No stains or smell are headed to the organic cotton zipper cover. Very pleased overall with the purchase and happy to take 5 minutes to add my review and hopefully have an impact on someone or a whole bunch of people's health. Shipping was super fast too. I couldn't have been happier!



