Thrilled with my purchase
My family and I live an organic lifestyle. It was important for me to have an organic mattress since we spend approximately 25 years of our life sleeping. Most non-organic mattresses contain chemicals and there are long-term health effects that may occur after prolonged exposure to these chemicals including cancers, damage to the heart, liver, central nervous system and kidneys. This is not something that I want my family breathing in every night. I did a lot of research and checked out all certifications. I found Plushbeds to be the best. 100% natural latex and organic with all certifications, including Greenguard Gold (not many mattresses have this, it was great to see). I ordered three of the 9" Botanical Bliss mattresses for all 3 bedrooms in our home. We received them 9 days after we placed the order and they were everything that we had hoped they would be. When we unwrapped the boxes, there were no odors at all. The mattresses were easy to set up and after 3 months of sleeping on them, we are thrilled! Very comfortable, feels great on my lower back and body. I sleep so well on this mattress. It feels great to go to sleep each night knowing that my family and I are not breathing in dangerous chemicals or fumes. We are very happy with Plushbeds and this mattress! 



