Why PlushBeds?

 

















S-Cape Adjustable Bed


Adjustable Mattress Foundation 

















































































































































				Create your perfect bedroom retreat with the S-Cape adjustable base. The S-Cape adjustable base lets you create your own personal escape with programmable positions and a one-touch flat button. 
			


Relax and Indulge in Luxurious Comfort
					The dual massage will soothe you as you rest, and help you ease tension in your body after a long day, while customizable positions ensure you get the rejuvenating environment you desire for any bedroom activity. Enhanced safety features make this luxurious adjustable base a great addition for your home.
				



Enjoy luxurious comfort and customize your sleep
					S-Cape Adjustable Beds allow you to elevate or lower your head and feet to maximize your own comfort level. Adjust your comfort at the touch of a button! With the touch of a button you will move into hundreds of relaxing positions. 
				



Control in the Palm of Your Hand
					All without creating stress or strain on your body, while your own personal massage system helps relieve tired sore muscles, and reduce everyday tension and fatigue. Transform your flat mattress to get more from your night and day. 
					
						Watch Video
					








Home > 
				Adjustable Beds > 
				S-Cape





*Mattresses and bed frames sold separately
































Please note: adjustable foundations can be used with any mattress and are therefore not returnable.

Compatible with all PlushBeds bedroom mattresses.
Includes wireless, stand-up remote.
Emergency power-down feature.
Press-and-hold safety flat feature.
Two programmable position buttons.
Head and foot articulation.
Dual massage with on-off button.
Contemporary gray patterned fabric.
4" legs with casters.
700 lb. total max lifting capacity.
Headboard bracket accessory kit available.






 

