Are the split king adjustable beds joined or must I find a way to keep them together?



Richard



                            on Aug 20, 2016
                        








BEST ANSWER: The king sized adjustable frame is (2) twin xls. Both sides are synced together to work as one unit and the frame holds both sides together so there is no gap in between the (2).The split king adjustable frame is also (2) twin xls. Each side has its own remote control and each side moves independently. Both sides can be synced together to use as one unit as well. You should order the same size mattress as the adjustable frame.

Reply

Inaccurate



            Dawn H
        

Staff
on Aug 21, 2016



















