The greatest bed ever.
I am a disabled Veteran with paraplegia and this bed is a life saver. I have endured five surgeries on my back and setting the bed the most comfortable after surgery is worth any price the bed may cost but fortunately the cost is very reasonable for what you get.  Complete adjustable ;for each partner in the bed. What more could you ask for? Why waste your money on another mattress when it will be worn out is six years and have to be replaced in about that time. I have mine for some 25 years & it still looks new plus it now has the new upgraded adjustable bed frame.



