Wonderful Addition To Our Bedroom!
We have been sleeping on our new S-Cape Adjustable bed for a little over one month and we wonder how we ever slept without it? There are so many nice features on this bed which really turn sleeping into a luxury experience. I like to move the head of the bed upwards to sit up and watch tv and also to read before bed. I also like to turn on the massage and it puts me to sleep at night - I have it set on a timer so it turns off on its own. If I had a hard day at work, I like to raise the foot of the bed to improve the circulation in my legs - it feels great. It comes with 2 lighted remote controls which is nice - you can adjust your position in the dark. We are extremely pleased with our purchase. I highly recommend this product if you want to enhance your sleeping experience and quality of life. Plushbeds was wonderful from beginning to end - very knowledgeable staff, they helped us select the perfect bed.  



